      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good list. i'm also seeing some people arguing that this kind of zoning is basically the only way to fix the housing crisis and make cities livable again, while others say it's kind of a disaster for local communities. do u think the critics have a point or are they just stuck in the past?",
