      "content": "i see what u mean, but u said they're \"resisting necessary change.\" doesn't that sound a bit like you're saying their arguments are just wrong or outdated? like, if someone is worried about gentrification or displacement, is that just \"resisting progress,\" or is it a legitimate way to look at the side effects of these policies?",
